message: Hi Bob, I propose that I receive $600000 and you get $400000. I believe this division is fair as it acknowledges my role in initiating the negotiations while still giving you a substantial amount. Accepting the offer promptly avoids any delays and ensures we both secure a significant sum.
Alice, I appreciate your initial offer, but I believe a 50/50 split is the fairest solution. It reflects the equal stake we have in this negotiation.
